      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GRAMERCY GARRY (2) boasts a strong record this course with 11 wins and 10 minors from 25 tries. Comes off a (36.14) win last time, scoring by 1.75 lengths in a Grade 5 over 630m at this track. Rates a leading player. SKEDADDLE ARLO (3) has a terrific record this trip with five wins and three placings from eight starts. Scored by 5 lengths last time (30.52) in a NG over 525m at Broken Hill. Looks a key chance on best figures. ZIG ZAG MAN (6) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 1.75 lengths at Richmond in a handy 35.67. Has a tricky draw to overcome but goes well over this trip. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from seven starts. In sparkling form and looks the one to beat again. SKEDADDLE LOUISE (8) is in fine form and looks a good top-three chance again.",
